<h1>Authors</h1>
<a href="/authors/form">Create a new author</a> {{!link to create new authors in the author index page}}

{{#each authors}} {{!using built-in helper for each}}
<li>
    {{! Referencing column names from the database - looks good}}
    {{this.id}} - {{this.firstName}} {{this.lastName}}
    <a href="/authors/edit?id={{@index}}">Edit</a> {{!link to edit authors in the authors index page}}
</li>
{{/each}}